  "detailed_description": "Many people are interested in Einstein's theory of relativity as I am, but its complicated mathematics keeps us out. This game provides us with an opportunity to intuitively experience the wonderful appearance of objects under general relativity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401150/extras/876d92ec46d7c610df17ae51d6d637b4.avif?t=1644456221\" width=562 height=162 /></span><br>In a world dominated by gravitation, all objects appear so symmetrical and elegant. Black holes are the most representative existence in this magnificent world.<br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br>1. Simulate the appearance of the black hole as accurately as possible.<br>2. You can adjust the parameters to change the appearance of the black hole.<br>3. You can also add a star to observe the interaction between the black hole and the star.<br>4. There are multiple space background sky boxes.<br>----------------- Update -----------------<br>5. Fly into the black hole, see the cosmic ball.",
  "about_the_game": "Many people are interested in Einstein's theory of relativity as I am, but its complicated mathematics keeps us out. This game provides us with an opportunity to intuitively experience the wonderful appearance of objects under general relativity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401150/extras/876d92ec46d7c610df17ae51d6d637b4.avif?t=1644456221\" width=562 height=162 /></span><br>In a world dominated by gravitation, all objects appear so symmetrical and elegant. Black holes are the most representative existence in this magnificent world.<br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br>1. Simulate the appearance of the black hole as accurately as possible.<br>2. You can adjust the parameters to change the appearance of the black hole.<br>3. You can also add a star to observe the interaction between the black hole and the star.<br>4. There are multiple space background sky boxes.<br>----------------- Update -----------------<br>5. Fly into the black hole, see the cosmic ball.",
